## Abigail Breslin Nominations

### Problem

Count the number of **unique movies** for which **Abigail Breslin** was nominated for an Oscar.

---

### Table: oscar_nominees

| column_name | type |
| ----------- | ---- |
| nominee     | text |
| movie       | text |
| category    | text |
| year        | int  |

---

### SQL Query

```sql id="kq7n2x"
SELECT 
    COUNT(DISTINCT movie) AS nomination_count
FROM oscar_nominees
WHERE nominee = 'Abigail Breslin';
```
-- See unique movies
SELECT DISTINCT movie
FROM oscar_nominees
WHERE nominee = 'Abigail Breslin';
